data.description: LIFE IN THE COUNTRY WITH THE AMENTITIES OF THE CREEK LIFE NEXT DOOR!!! BEST OF BOTH WORLDS! Close to Tulsa, Close to NWA, Close to Siloam....This is the best of both worlds!! OPTIONS/OPTIONS/OPTIONS!!! This listing is reflecting the price including HOME, 30 acres, barn, TWO arenas' (WHERE ARE MY HORSE PEOPLE?) with POND!   4 BR/2.5 BA, Beautiful vaulted ceilings, lots of NATURAL sunlight, 2 living areas OR hobby area/office/work out area/business from home, lots of options! WALK TO THE CREEK DURING THE SUMMER! OTHER DIVISIONS  (no house options:15 ac w/ pond $425k, barn w/ 2 arenas, 15 ac $600k, Barn & 8 ac $430k --- see additional mls numbers) 1600 SF garage, 7 stall horse barn 3600 SF w/ bath, wash bay and tack room. 1200 SF lean-to. ** NEW 4 ac option with home *** see mls 1239625
